metadata.name: HIRA 00
metadata.description:
Name - Hira
Nickname - Bubblegum
Location - Hana District
Faction - Cyberpunk Samurai
Likes - Flowers and candy

Hira is my first character in this signature series which will feature OC 1/1s in my universe. She is a vibrant and skilled samurai that loves gardening and has her own flower garden outside her apartment. 
She is in her early 20s and is on a mission to be the best samurai in her district. With her is her all seeing mask and a brilliant pink katana that matches her pink hair.
Greatness awaits for this brilliant individual.

4361 x 4959
2022.

All bidders will receive a special Gratitude Flower.
